<br>
It always has been better to take up to a full group though.  Produce a higher killrate which will offset the lower loot to person ratio.<br>
<br>
I've spent more hours in that god forsaken zone than I'd like to count now so I obviously know it quite well. If it's your first trip there do not try to duo it. You'll have a horrible CR ahead of you. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
